### **Phase 7: Rendering Strategy**

**Not all pages deserve the same rendering:**

| Page Type | Strategy | Revalidation | Why |
|-----------|----------|--------------|-----|
| **Verses** | ISR | 24 hours | Content stable, high traffic |
| **Topics** | ISR | 7 days | Updated weekly |
| **Study Plans** | ISR | 30 days | Rarely change |
| **User Content** | Dynamic | N/A | Real-time updates |
| **Static Pages** | SSG | Never | Never change |

**Balance:**
- ‚ùå Overusing SSG ‚Üí Builds time out
- ‚ùå Overusing Dynamic ‚Üí Hurts crawlability
- ‚úÖ ISR with long revalidation = Best of both worlds

